_:N81fd505411dc43d884599801a8688e3d <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Cabinet Office press office only deals with enquiries from the media.</p>\n\n<p>If you are not a member of the media, please use the public correspondence <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/contact-the-cabinet-office\" class=\"govuk-link\">contact form</a>.</p>\n\n<p>If you are a journalist with a press enquiry or interview request, please email our <a href=\"mailto:pressoffice@cabinetoffice.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">press office</a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p>Please note, if you have a media query concerning the Prime Minister or media access to Downing Street - please call the press office for No10 Downing Street.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
